Hardware Requirements
Minimum 2GB RAM (configurable), more the better for higher rewards
Internet connectivity available 24/7
Software Requirements for PC Users
For Windows Install WSL - https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/windows/wsl/install#install-wsl-command

For Windows Install Ubuntu after Installing WSL - https://apps.microsoft.com/detail/9PDXGNCFSCZV?hl=en-us&gl=IN&ocid=pdpshare

For macOS If you have Installed Homebrew (https://brew.sh/) to manage packages on OS X, run this command to install Git.

brew install git
